## -----------------------------------------------------------------------
## These flags are passed to the Erlang VM when running `bin/rlm remote`,
## `bin/rlm rpc`, or other commands that connect to the running node.
## -----------------------------------------------------------------------

## Use a hidden node for remote connections so they don't join the
## full mesh and interfere with the running cluster.
## (The release boot script already sets --hidden, but this is explicit.)

## Keep the distribution buffer modest for the remote shell.
+zdbbl 1024

## Reduce the async thread pool for the lightweight remote VM.
+A 1
